Title: Designates a portion of the state highway system as the Trooper Joseph J. Gallagher Memorial Bridge
Summary: Designates a portion of the state highway system on the Long Island Expressway, county of Suffolk, as the "Trooper Joseph J. Gallagher Memorial Bridge".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Trooper Joseph J. Gallagher Memorial Bridge"
